{"tid":453598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳凱文史貝西桃色事件導致《紙牌屋》被正式腰斬","createTime":"2017-10-31T10:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T12:40:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d19946440b3f8a205b0d34427134f2e3b0d7b0c8","tid":453598,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡影帝凱文史貝西（Kevin Spacey）被指控性騷擾事件後不到一天，Netflix 宣布取消原創影集《紙牌屋》（House of Cards），將於明年播出的第六季成為最終季。<br />\n <br />\nNetflix 與《紙牌屋》的製作公司 Media Rights Capital 發表聲明表示，凱文史貝西昨晚的新聞深深地困擾著他們。為了對此做出回應，他們抵達巴爾的摩與該劇演員、工作人員進行會面，確保他們能繼續感到安全與支持。依照先前的行程安排，凱文史貝西現在還未開始在片場展開拍攝。<br />\n <br />\n乍看之下， Netflix 取消《紙牌屋》的決定與凱文史貝西性騷擾事件有關，但根據 TVLine 的報導指出，該決定其實在多個月前就已確定，並非因凱文史貝西的事件所影響，而 Netflix 代表方隨後也證實此消息的真實性。<br />\n <br />\n《紙牌屋》第六季兩周前開拍，將於 2018 年首播。（ew、TVLine）[/quote]"},{"pid":"12639adc47ad0944be51fddf553dafb596684fd9","tid":453598,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"我第一季都未睇完<br />\n睇侵侵真人show好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230f5c8967a46df81b5392180b9f77b7ec0734c3","tid":453598,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"Spacey:I'm gay,don't blame me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2ce5e95a6a217c759180899566bf5323ab363a","tid":453598,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"換總統一角咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字試用版</ins><br />\n<br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg